               <msContents>
                  <summary>Amharic Commentary on the Introductory Rite to the Miracles of Mary, Miracles of Mary, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተአምረ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>, Layman's Prayer, in Amharic</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="44v" facs="001">Fols 1r–44v</locus>
                      <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5933CommMuallaqa">Amharic
                                                  Commentary on the Introductory Rite to the
                                                  Miracles of Mary</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Amharic and Gǝʿǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="45r" to="51r" facs="045">Fols 45r–51r</locus>
                    <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2384Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  Māryām</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1"><locus from="45r" facs="045">Fols 45r and following</locus><title>King Marǝqos (Mark) who abandoned his throne for monastic life</title></msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2"><locus from="47r" facs="047">Fols 47r and following</locus><title>How Our Lord and the Apostle built the first church dedicated to Mary and how, on the occasion, the Lord ordained Peter head of the Apostles, arsäy astäfanos</title></msItem>
                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3"><locus from="49r" facs="049">Fols 49r and following</locus><title>What will happen when the Lord comes for the second time</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="Gez">
                          ተአምሪሃ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ስምዑ፡ አበውየ፡ ወአኃውየ፡ ዘንተ፡፡መሥጢረ፡ ወመድምመ፡ ዘነገሩነ፡ አበዊነ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ቅዱሳን፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ውይቤሉ፡ አመ፡ ይመጽእ፡ እግዚእነ፡ በዳግም፡ ምጽአቱ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                        </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                      </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                    <locus from="51r" to="53v" facs="051">Fols 51r–53v</locus>
                    <textLang mainLang="am"/>
                    <title>Layman’s prayer, in Amharic, Addamǝn, or Noḫǝn, expanded</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="am">
                      እግዚአብሔር፡ ርኅሩኃ፡ ልብ፡ አድኅነኒ፡ አዳምን፡ ከሲኦል፡ ንኖን፡ ከማየ፡ አይህ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
